arStrings.szText: For my son, if my spirit leaves my body and I join our ancestors before I can speak with you, below is what I leave you.

Four silver cups, to use when life gives you turbulence. My child nor his children will ever go hungry. Most importantly, I leave you the roof that housed you as a babe and will house your future partner and children. Let the hearth bring you warmth in the coldest of nights.
